CUSTOMIZATION INSTRUCTIONS/CHOOSING YOUR INITIALS ——— 1) Click on CUSTOMIZE ———— 2) In the LAYERS area you’ll see separate rows from A to Z for all of the CENTER, LEFT and RIGHT initials as well as the ORIGINAL ad example initials which are visible on top and in the workspace . Place the cursor over each of the original initial layers, click on the little icon on the right, and they will become INVISIBLE. ——– 3) Then scroll down to the CENTER initial you want, click on the little icon on the right to make it VISIBLE (all A-Z initials are all initially hidden and INVISIBLE).
